here all night

288
00:17:01,625 --> 00:17:03,166
and you never
would have hit it.

289
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:06,250
What the heck...?

290
00:17:06,333 --> 00:17:09,833
Some genius dropped
a hairclip! Ow...

291
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:13,250
