311
00:18:28,541 --> 00:18:30,291
Show your true self!

312
00:18:30,375 --> 00:18:32,416
Why? Curious?

313
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:36,083
I must rid the world of spirits
who defile the natural order.

314
00:18:36,166 --> 00:18:38,083
You're funny.

315
00:18:45,333 --> 00:18:47,958
Are you the one responsible
for unleashing this havoc?

316
00:18:48,041 --> 00:18:50,291
That's one way of
putting it, I guess...

317
00:18:50,375 --> 00:18:53,125
Spirits are attracted to
the power of my stones.

318
00:18:53,208 --> 00:18:54,125
Really?

319
00:18:54,208 --> 00:18:57,875
That's right...
My Bane Stones.

320
00:19:09,958 --> 00:19:12,250
